Blackfang nodded at Shadow and quickly ran inside.

He stopped when he saw Cam, her back to him, speaking with 
Nightlight. He motionned Nightlight not to signal him by putting a 
finger to where his mouth could have been. He readied a gruffy 
paternal voice and said:

Blackfang: AH-HA! You didn't eat the green things, did you? (His 
tone was still playful) I knew it! Come and give me a hug, you 
little houndbot Cam!

He kneeled and opened his arms.
